*xoops-2.2.1 (09 Aug 2005)

  09 Aug 2005; Renat Lumpau <rl03@gentoo.org> files/postinstall-en.txt,
  -xoops-2.0.13.ebuild, +xoops-2.2.1.ebuild:
  Version bump wrt security bug #101899. Removed vulnerable versions.

*xoops-2.0.13 (03 Jul 2005)

  03 Jul 2005; Renat Lumpau <rl03@gentoo.org>
  -files/xoops-2.0.9.2-fix-file-ext-validation.diff,
  files/postinstall-en.txt, -xoops-2.0.7.3.ebuild, -xoops-2.0.9.2.ebuild,
  -xoops-2.0.12a.ebuild, +xoops-2.0.13.ebuild:
  Version bump (#79348). Fixes XML_RPC vulnerability (#97399).

*xoops-2.0.12a (30 Jun 2005)

  30 Jun 2005; Aaron Walker <ka0ttic@gentoo.org> +xoops-2.0.12a.ebuild:
  Version bump for security bug 97522.

  11 Mar 2005; Jan Brinkmann <luckyduck@gentoo.org> xoops-2.0.9.2.ebuild:
  added ~amd64 to KEYWORDS. fixes #84443

*xoops-2.0.9.2 (11 Mar 2005)

  11 Mar 2005; Aaron Walker <ka0ttic@gentoo.org>
  +files/xoops-2.0.9.2-fix-file-ext-validation.diff, +xoops-2.0.9.2.ebuild:
  Version bump; added patch to fix weak file extension validation (see bug
  84570) until upstream releases a new version.

  18 Oct 2004; David Holm <dholm@gentoo.org> xoops-2.0.7.3.ebuild:
  Added to ~ppc.

*xoops-2.0.7.3 (22 Sep 2004)

